c74object.name: bruits.warps~
c74object.digest: Mutable Instruments warps wrapped as max/msp
c74object.description:
Mutable Instruments warps wrapped as max/msp.
see https://mutable-instruments.net/modules/warps/

attribute.name: carrier_drive
attribute.digest: Control the amplitude of the carrier
attribute.description: Control the amplitude of the carrier.

attribute.name: timbre
attribute.digest: controls the intensity of the high harmonics created by cross-modulation - or provides another dimension of tone control for some algorithms
attribute.description: controls the intensity of the high harmonics created by cross-modulation - or provides another dimension of tone control for some algorithms.

attribute.name: modulator_drive
attribute.digest: Control the amplitude of the modulator
attribute.description: Control the amplitude of the modulator.

attribute.name: oscillator_state
attribute.digest: Enables the internal oscillator and selects its waveform
attribute.description: Enables the internal oscillator and selects its waveform

attribute.name: algorithm
attribute.digest: Selects which signal processing operation is performed on the carrier and modulator
attribute.description: Selects which signal processing operation is performed on the carrier and modulator.
